Paano mo naman hindi maibibigay?

492
00:30:18,279 --> 00:30:19,240
Li Youen, subukan mo lang

493
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:20,759
Wala bang kasabihan?

494
00:30:20,759 --> 00:30:21,920
Huwag makinig sa sinasabi niya

495
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:22,960
Tingnan kung ano ang ginagawa niya

496
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,079
Kaya kong gawin ang kahit ano

497
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,440
Gagawin ko ito para sa iyo ngayon

498
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:27,640
Gagawin ko ito para sa iyo.

499
00:30:28,119 --> 00:30:28,799
Ano ang tinitingnan mo?

500
00:30:28,799 --> 00:30:29,559
Gagawin ko ito para sa iyo.

501
00:30:29,559 --> 00:30:30,559
Nag-aaway sila!

502
00:30:41,559 --> 00:30:42,279
Naku hindi!

503
00:30:43,359 --> 00:30:44,160
Sira na lahat!

504
00:30:44,319 --> 00:30:45,079
Ako...

505
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,559
Hindi ko sinasadya.

506
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:47,920
Huwag ka sanang magalit.

507
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,119
Alam kong pangit ako sa paningin.

508
00:30:55,319 --> 00:30:56,359
Mawawala ako ngayon din.

509
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,839
Pupunta ako sa bodega.

510
00:30:59,359 --> 00:31:00,319
Huminahon ka.

511
00:31:11,319 --> 00:31:12,319
Bakit ka tumatakbo?

512
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:13,759
Ayaw ba ni Teacher Li na nandito tayo?

513
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,880
Nakikita mo ba kung gaano ka-sunud-sunuran si Matandang Zhai?

514
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:16,640
Malamang,

515
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:17,799
masasangkot din tayo nito.

516
00:31:18,039 --> 00:31:18,480
Kaya,

517
00:31:19,039 --> 00:31:20,279
talagang hindi tayo maaaring makita.

518
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,359
May katuturan iyan.

519
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:32,559
Kung tatakbo tayo ulit,

520
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:35,079
Sasamahan kitang tumakas.

521
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,960
Parang isang matigas ang ulong taliptip

522
00:31:47,039 --> 00:31:48,160
Hindi kita kayang ipaglaban

523
00:31:49,559 --> 00:31:50,920
Ang kapatid mo ang magbubuhat ng tela

524
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:52,839
Kaya mo bang ilipat ang tela?

525
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,039
O magmaneho ng trak

526
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,160
Kung gayon, hindi mo na kailangang pumunta

527
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,279
Ikaw ang hindi dapat pumunta

528
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:58,759
Kapatid

529
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:00,960
Dapat kang pumunta

530
00:32:01,359 --> 00:32:02,400
Hindi ka kailangan dito

531
00:32:02,759 --> 00:32:04,640
Kailangan kita, kailangan mo ako

532
00:32:05,039 --> 00:32:05,839
Pumunta ka lang

533
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:06,480
Isama mo ako

534
00:32:06,559 --> 00:32:08,119
Ayaw ng boss na 'yan sa mga nahuhuli

535
00:32:10,359 --> 00:32:10,880
Kapatid

536
00:32:11,039 --> 00:32:11,839
Tingnan mo siya

537
00:32:36,799 --> 00:32:37,240
Tara na

538
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:38,640
Tara

539
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:39,680
gawin ito

540
00:32:40,039 --> 00:32:41,079
Ito ang aking lugar

541
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:43,599
Kaya saan ako uupo?

542
00:32:43,599 --> 00:32:44,839
Sino ang may pakialam sa iyo?

543
00:32:46,359 --> 00:32:47,720
Puno na ang mga puting tela

544
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,079
Magiging overload ito kung uupo ang mga tao

545
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:51,920
Hindi mo ibig sabihin na gusto mo ang kapatid ko.

546
00:32:52,319 --> 00:32:53,880
magkamali, ikaw ba?

547
00:32:59,039 --> 00:33:01,039
Kaya ano ang gusto mo kung ganoon?

548
00:33:01,799 --> 00:33:02,839
Dapat bumalik ka na lang.

549
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,960
Atleta ka ba?

550
00:33:05,119 --> 00:33:05,720
Ang maliit na bahagi ng kalsadang ito,

551
00:33:06,079 --> 00:33:07,880
dahil sa iyong karaniwang dami ng pagsasanay,

552
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:09,559
hindi dapat malaki para sa iyo.

553
00:33:09,799 --> 00:33:10,400
Ikaw

554
00:33:10,559 --> 00:33:11,319
Anong ibig mong sabihin, 'ikaw'?

555
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,079
Ayaw mo ba akong sundan mismo?

556
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,839
Sinabi ko na sa iyo,

557
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:22,680
wala nang espasyo sa loob ng kotse,

558
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:23,640
at sinabihan kang huwag kang sumama.

559
00:33:23,759 --> 00:33:24,279
Xiao Si,

560
00:33:24,279 --> 00:33:25,079
tara na.

561
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:25,759
Ako

562
00:33:25,759 --> 00:33:26,519
Paalam

563
00:33:29,720 --> 00:33:30,519
Youen

564
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:31,640
Pag-usapan natin itong muli

565
00:33:33,759 --> 00:33:34,559
Youen

566
00:33:40,039 --> 00:33:40,759
Kapatid

567
00:33:41,079 --> 00:33:43,559
Ang mga taong maawain ay magdudulot ng malaking kasawian

568
00:34:04,319 --> 00:34:05,319
Walang espasyo sa kotse

569
00:34:05,319 --> 00:34:06,680
Sinabi ko na sa'yo na huwag kang sumama

570
00:34:08,679 --> 00:34:09,480
Li Youen

571
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:13,119
Saan ba talaga walang lugar

572
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:46,320
Bakit bigla na lang umuulan nang napakalakas?

573
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:48,920
Iniisip ko kung may masisilungan ba siya mula sa ulan.

574
00:34:49,119 --> 00:34:50,360
Kung hindi, sige na nga.

575
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:52,440
Malakas at malusog siya.

576
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:53,800
Hindi naman siya masasaktan kahit mabasa lang nang kaunti.

577
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,079
Ang lakas ng ulan...

578
00:34:55,519 --> 00:34:57,239
Kahit ang pinakamalusog na tao ay maaaring magkasakit.

579
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,320
Hindi, hindi niya gagawin.

580
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,679
Binuhusan ko siya ng tubig noong umagang iyon.

581
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:01,880
At maayos naman siya.

582
00:35:02,639 --> 00:35:03,599
Bakit mo siya binuhusan ng tubig?

583
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,639
Umakyat siya sa kama mo!

584
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:28,079
Nakabalik na ako.

585
00:35:31,079 --> 00:35:32,639
Hindi ko talaga alam kung saan ako magtatago mula sa ulan.

586
00:35:38,079 --> 00:35:38,880
Li Youen

587
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,199
Nakabalik na ako.

588
00:35:48,199 --> 00:35:49,400
Mahaba ang daan na iyon,

589
00:35:50,559 --> 00:35:52,159
pero naglakad pa rin ako pabalik.

590
00:35:54,559 --> 00:35:56,239
Gusto ko lang ipangako sa iyo

591
00:35:57,559 --> 00:35:58,840
Babayaran kita.

592
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,320
Makikinig ako sa iyo.

593
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,039
Kahit ano pa ang hilingin mo sa akin,

594
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,920
kahit anong landas ang gusto mong tahakin ko,

595
00:36:09,519 --> 00:36:11,360
Tatahakin ko ito tulad ngayon,

596
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,280
nang walang pag-aalinlangan.

597
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,880
Pero may isang bagay:

598
00:36:23,639 --> 00:36:25,079
Huwag mo akong piliting iwan ka.

599
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:45,079
Pero may isang bagay

600
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,159
Huwag mo akong hayaang iwan ka.

601
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,719
Zhai Qiuyu,

602
00:36:57,119 --> 00:36:58,159
Ang ingay-ingay mo!

603
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,559
Kapatid,

604
00:37:12,559 --> 00:37:13,360
Umaga.

605
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:41,039
Xiao Si,

606
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,000
Pupunta na ba tayo?

607
00:37:42,159 --> 00:37:42,800
Sige.

608
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,039
Kapatid.
